Commercial Laundry Sales, Installation and Parts in South Carolina
 




Service Laundry Machinery has been providing sales, installation, service and parts for a variety of laundry equipment manufacturers for the last 35 years. We are proud to be a Dexter authorized distributor, and we are ready to help with your coin, card or on-premise laundry needs. Contact us today to find out how we can help make your laundry a success!
 



























