Who sold SLM Corporation stock? Who is selling SLM Corporation stock?

SLM Corporation's stock was sold by a variety of institutional investors in the last quarter, including Oakbrook Investments LLC. Company insiders that have sold SLM Corporation stock in the last year include Laurent Charles Lutz and Paul F Thome. View Insider Buying and Selling for SLM Corporation.



Who bought SLM Corporation stock? Who is buying SLM Corporation stock?

SLM Corporation's stock was purchased by a variety of institutional investors in the last quarter, including Rockefeller Financial Services Inc., Aperio Group LLC and Capstone Asset Management Co.. Company insiders that have bought SLM Corporation stock in the last two years include Earl A Goode, Jeffrey Dale, Laurent Charles Lutz, Marianne M Keler, Raymond J Quinlan, Robert S Strong and Steven Mcgarry. View Insider Buying and Selling for SLM Corporation.



How do I buy SLM Corporation stock? 

Shares of SLM Corporation can be purchased through any online brokerage account. Popular online brokerages include Vanguard Brokerage Services, TD Ameritrade, E*TRADE, Scottrade, Fidelity and Charles Schwab. 



